<seg id="154">Due to this, the construction of the border section did not achieve the national goal of improving the connection between Prague and Usti nad Labem.</seg>
<seg id="155">The RMD subjected the border section No 0807 of the D 8 and the section No 0805 by the Bohemian Central Mountains to a profitability study between 1999 and 2001.</seg>
