<seg id="852">Concluding remark</seg>
<seg id="853">The cooperation achieved the goals of the BRH and the NKÚ.</seg>
<seg id="854">Both audit offices gained in-depth knowledge of VAT management systems in the Czech Republic and Germany.</seg>
<seg id="855">The cooperation disclosed differences in the two systems and in the statutory provisions governing the VAT administration.</seg>
<seg id="856">During the parallel tests, interesting cases of intra-Community deliveries or acquisitions occurred.</seg>
<seg id="857">For some of them, another observation is worthwhile.</seg>
<seg id="858">On the basis of the audit results, both Court of Auditors produced recommendations for the management of VAT.</seg>
<seg id="859">Follow-up of these recommendations in the form of an audit should be part of the follow-up.</seg>
<seg id="860">The new experience and knowledge gained through the cooperation of both Court of Auditors is the basis for the successful execution of future VAT management audits.</seg>
